column2: Throw a blade at your foe that causes damage over time. If activated again, your target is pulled to you. If your target gets too far away before the blade is pulled, the effect is removed.
Makes volatile beetles inert. Also, launches you backward at an alarming rate.
Launch a phosphorous mortar round that burns brightly at impact point.

Minions deal more damage and take conditions from you. When a minion attacks, it transfers conditions to its target.
There is a 10 second cooldown per minion.
Your power is increased. Gain additional power while wielding a greatsword. Your greatsword skills have reduced recharge.
Catch as many insects as you can in two minutes!
Using a deception ability removes revealed. Reduces recharge on deception skills.

Double-click to gain a hero point.
This...food has an unfamiliar but tempting aroma. Probably best to eat it first and not ask questions.
Gain retaliation when you activate a <c=@abilitytype>Virtue</c>. Retaliation you grant has increased duration.
Gather Mordrem samples from the vine chambers.

Double-click to gain a hero point.
The hottest, spiciest food in all of Tyria—it's guaranteed to make smoke come out of your ears...

Complete Daily Recommended Fractals to obtain Fractal Research Pages. Combine the pages into a completed journal and exchange it for a Thaumonova Fractal Research Paper from the Thaumanova Field Researcher located at the end of the Thaumanova Reactor fractal.
Deploy bombs at the supply depot that will explode if the objective is captured by an enemy team. The explosion will destroy all remaining supply at the objective.
Launch a mortar round that spreads poisonous gas in an area.

Deal more damage while downed. Inflict vulnerability when you strike a foe below the health threshold.
Cannot apply vulnerability the same target more than once per interval.
A recipe to make an ascended medium breather with Assassin (+Precision, +Power, and +Ferocity) stats.
Gain stealth when you use a healing skill.
<c=@abilitytype>Legendary Centaur.</c> Will the tablet toward the target location. As the tablet moves, it will heal allies it passes through.
The primary Pact rally point has fallen to the Mordrem.
Activate this Tactic to make the next set of dolyaks invincible, guaranteeing that they will reach their destination.
Used in crafting ascended backpacks. Made of damask, elonian leather, spiritwood, and Deldrimor steel.
Entering shroud grants swiftness and removes movement-impairing conditions.
Gain might when you strike a foe below the health threshold.
Follow the trail Rox left for you so you can reunite with your team.

Spawns a guild banner that will give +10%% karma, +15%% magic find, +10%% experience from kills, +10%% gold from kills, +10%% increased movement speed, and +15%% gathering chance to any ally that touches it for 30 minutes. Does not stack with other banner boosts.

Obtain the Gigantic Ice Elemental Core from the remains of the giant ice elemental in Wayfarer Foothills. Bring it to the heart of the volcano core inside the Fractals of the Mists and imbue it in the lava. 
This item only has value as part of a collection.
Drop bandages when you use a tool belt skill.
A recipe to make an ascended light breather with Soldier (+Power, +Vitality, and +Toughness) stats.
Create two rifts, one above and one below your target. After a short delay, these rifts will create a barrier from the Mists, preventing foes from crossing.
A recipe to make an ascended heavy breather with Sentinel (+Vitality, +Power, and +Toughness) stats.
Chest[s] of the Elite Fractal Veteran
Purchased with Pristine Fractal Relics from BUY-2046 PFR in Mistlock Observatory.
Call a mortar strike on target area.

Project Ventari's tablet into the world. The tablet will heal allies near it every few seconds.
(The tablet will disappear if you move outside the tether distance.)

Double-click to gain a hero point.
This potent drink is only served at the Last Whiskey Bar. They say it can curl your whiskers.
Gain a boon upon casting a <c=@abilitytype>glyph</c> based on your attunement. <c=@abilitytype>Glyphs</c> gain reduced recharge.
Malchor's Leap: Cathedral of Eternal Radiance
Gain fury when you strike a foe that has burning stacks over the threshold.
Your turrets are surrounded by a reflective shield when built. Turrets deal more damage and have a longer attack range.
A recipe to make an ascended light breather with Cleric (+Healing Power, +Power, and +Toughness) stats.
Smash the ground in front of you to damage foes. After a delay, allies in the area are healed. Heals for more if an enemy was struck.

Double-click to gain a hero point.
A savage concoction created by Wolf shamans, this is guaranteed to make you howl.
Regain opening strike whenever you gain fury. Opening strike deals more damage.
<c=@abilitytype>Phantasms</c> take your conditions when they are first summoned.
Cast enfeebling blood when you hit a foe.
Fields of Ruin: The Ogre Road
You've died in this instance and may not reenter it.

Map completion is another way to explore Tyria. Find all waypoints, points of interest, and vistas and complete all renown hearts and hero challenges in a map to earn rewards. Your completion progress is on your map.

Double-click to gain a hero point.
A special Canthan recipe. Centuries old.

Double-click to summon this mini to follow you around. Only one mini may be in use at a time.
Combine 3 of this mini with a Pile of Crystalline Dust, an Obsidian Shard, and an Azure Denaturizing Agent (dropped by creatures in scale 21–50 fractals) in the Mystic Forge to create a Mini Baron von Scrufflebutt.
Straits of Devastation: Half Circle Cove
Found in Chests of the Mists and salvaged from ascended rings. Used to stabilize dark energy for the safe construction of items. Can also be traded for Fractal Encryptions.
Consume conditions to gain health when you use a healing skill.

A scaling five-man dungeon displaced by time and space that grants players greater rewards as they delve deeper into the Mists.
Players must be level 80 to enter.
<c=@abilitytype>Trap.</c> Lay a trap that deals damage and unleashes multiple fragments into the area when triggered. Each fragment grants aegis to allies, as long as they don't already have aegis.
A recipe to make an ascended medium breather with Apothecary (+Healing Power, +Toughness, and +Condition Damage) stats.
